OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FAn American anti-Islam influencer due
OL,7,Fto speak at a rally organised by Tommy
OL,8,FRobinson has been blocked from
OL,9,Fentering the UK by the home secretary.
OL,11,FValentina Gomez was due to attend the
OL,12,FUnite the Kingdom rally in May, and
OL,13,Fhad shared a screenshot online of an
OL,14,Femail showing her granted electronic
OL,15,Ftravel authorisation (ETA), prompting
OL,16,Fbacklash from MPs and campaign groups.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
