FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FThe government has blocked her entry
OL,7,Fto the country over concerns her
OL,8,Fpresence would not be conducive to the
OL,9,Fpublic good - the same justification
OL,10,Fused for blocking rapper Kanye West
OL,11,Fearlier this month.
OL,13,FGomez was excluded from the UK on the
OL,14,Fgrounds that the democratic right to
OL,15,Fexpression does not extend to
OL,16,Fpromoting hatred and extremism, it is
OL,17,Funderstood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
