PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,F"People who propagate hate speech and
OL,7,Fdivision should not be given free
OL,8,Fentry to the United Kingdom," the
OL,9,FMuslim Council of Britain said on
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,12,F"This decision is the right course of
OL,13,Faction by the UK government, and this
OL,14,Fshould be a precedent for others who
OL,15,Fchoose to promote disinformation and
OL,16,Fhatred."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
