OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FGomez, who has more than 540,000
OL,7,Ffollowers on Instagram, gained
OL,8,Fnotoriety through a series of anti-
OL,9,FIslamist and anti-LGBTQ+ stunts,
OL,10,Fincluding using a flamethrower to burn
OL,11,Fboth the Quran and LGBTQ+ inclusive
OL,12,Fbooks.
OL,14,FLast year, Gomez called for the UK to
OL,15,Fappoint a prime minister who would
OL,16,Fsend Muslims "back to their Sharia
OL,17,Fnations" while speaking at Unite the
OL,18,FKingdom, an anti-immigration march,
OL,19,Falongside Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
