PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FBaroness Shaista Gohir urged the
OL,7,Fgovernment to deny Gomez entry on
OL,8,FSunday, sharing a statement on X from
OL,9,Fthe charity the Muslim Women's Network
OL,10,FUK.
OL,12,FGomez responded to the statement by
OL,13,Fwriting: "If you keep speaking without
OL,14,Fbeing spoken to, I'll have your
OL,15,Fhusband mohamed discipline you."
OL,17,F"Others have been denied entry to the
OL,18,FUK for rhetoric directed at other
OL,19,Ffaith groups," the Muslim Council of
OL,20,FBritain wrote in its letter to Mahmood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
