PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,F"The inconsistency raises serious
OL,7,Fconcerns about whose speech is deemed
OL,8,Funacceptable and whose is permitted".
OL,10,FRapper West, who also goes by the name
OL,11,FYe, made an application to travel to
OL,12,Fthe UK earlier this month after he was
OL,13,Fbooked to headline the London festival
OL,14,FWireless.
OL,16,FHis application was blocked on the
OL,17,Fgrounds that his presence would not be
OL,18,Fconducive to the public good,
OL,19,Ffollowing his history of antisemitism.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
