PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776708665
OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FThe rapper has voiced admiration for
OL,7,FAdolf Hitler and made numerous
OL,8,Fantisemitic remarks in the recent
OL,9,Fpast, including releasing a song
OL,10,Fcalled Heil Hitler and advertising a
OL,11,Fswastika T-shirt for sale.
OL,13,FIn January, he took out a full-page
OL,14,Fadvert in the Wall Street Journal to
OL,15,Fapologise for his actions, titled: "To
OL,16,FThose I've Hurt", where he blamed his
OL,17,Fbipolar disorder, linked to an
OL,18,Fundiagnosed brain injury.
