OL,3,CAnti-Islam influencer blocked from
OL,4,Centering UK for Tommy Robinson rally
OL,6,FLast week, Homelessness charity
OL,7,FCentrepoint cut ties with TV
OL,8,Fpersonality Sharon Osbourne after she
OL,9,Fexpressed support for the Unite the
OL,10,FKingdom rally in May.
OL,12,FThe march, organised by Robinson, was
OL,13,Flast attended by between 110,000 and
OL,14,F150,000 people in September.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
